snippet.title: Uri Avenged: Indian Commandos Gun Down More Than 38 Terrorists Inside PoK

localized.description:
Indian Army conducted surgical strikes on terror launch pads at the LoC on Wednesday, the DGMO said on Thursday in a press briefing. Surgical strikes were based on specific intelligence inputs of terror groups ready to infiltrate into India and carry out terror attacks.
